,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:41:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一開始只買盤<br />\n開始贏夠一定數目<br />\n就大注買d低賠率既主客和當收息<br />\n但要小心唔好買d出名假既聯賽<br />\n因為真係假到你唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係話反駁你<br />\n不過我身邊就有個朋友係咁<br />\n日賭夜賭賺少少 之後買場1.1x倍嘅話當收息<br />\n爆冷一舖輸返晒又可以開月光寶盒再黎過</blockquote><br />\n最On9就係買啲所謂嘅收息波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n法國對盧森堡 主勝1.001 都試過開唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 收息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只買西甲 德甲 意甲  <br />\n最多之前買埋荷甲<br />\n不過燕好分末落了<br />\n同埋點會買1.0幾個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只會見到巴塞個d有1.1幾至1.2幾先會買"},{"pid":"80d91967aebc67bee6501df61673f68853476c87","tid":482712,"uid":123137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:41:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>贏左自然會心雄<br />\n自自然然會輸返/倒輸<br />\n識收手先叫贏錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n心態&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;技術<br />\n同枱食飯，各自修行<br />\n唔好場場買,個個人睇盤方法唔同,你見到人場場買都中,唔代表佢長期贏錢<br />\n<br />\n有信心先好買,同埋最好平注<br />\n<br />\n以前都係輸錢多<br />\n呢一兩年算係每個月執少少"},{"pid":"4cd813ea87b14fb24c13e58d3a507498dcbdf970","tid":482712,"uid":123137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:47:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>贏左自然會心雄<br />\n自自然然會輸返/倒輸<br />\n識收手先叫贏錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比D規則自己<br />\nEG.連輸3場,休息幾日咁樣<br />\n多數輸錢就會想追數,理性自然會消失"},{"pid":"0bf9737ad9e96875aee5745215073fa00e655d05","tid":482712,"uid":107472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:49:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>贏左自然會心雄<br />\n自自然然會輸返/倒輸<br />\n識收手先叫贏錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></bloc